br.com.caelum.vraptor.proxy

Class CDIProxies

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.caelum.vraptor.proxy.CDIProxies

  • public final class CDIProxies
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class to work with CDI proxies, allowing us to get objects without weld proxies. At this time this class only works with JBoss Weld, but since Weld is the only one that implements CDI 1.1, this is not a big trouble.
